Notable Projects

Colorado Park Rangers


https://github.com/dawsontc003/CO_Park_Rangers

https://dawsontc003.github.io/CO_Park_Rangers

This is an informational application. This application can be utilized for any one who is interested in National Parks in the State of Colorado. This application will provide you with not only the location and hours of the national parks but it also will provide a list of activities that are available at each park.

Budget Tracker


https://github.com/dawsontc003/budget-tracker

https://limitless-citadel-07996.herokuapp.com/

This application is all about documenting transactions. This application provides a ledger where both revenue and expenses can be tracked. The real power of this application comes into play when a user is offline. One can not only still access the application but also input tranactions and soon as the application is back online any submitted transactions will be sent to the database.

Workout Tracker


https://github.com/dawsontc003/workout-tracker

https://cryptic-beyond-51250.herokuapp.com/

This application is a simple workout tracker. Users can enter a given excercise and not only track that workout but record the workout and pick up from a stopping point and continue. The application will track reps as well as time.

Discover Your Inner-Animal


https://github.com/dawsontc003/discover-your-animal/

https://sleepy-sierra-89293.herokuapp.com/

The Inner-Animal application is a fun website that allows a user to answer a series of personality questions. Once the questions are submitted the application will evaluate the users responses and compare the evaluation outcome to a set scores table. Once compared to the scores table the user will be presente with an animal image that matches their personality.

Note Taker


https://github.com/dawsontc003/note-taker/

https://shielded-everglades-01019.herokuapp.com/

This is an application that anyone can find useful. This Note Taker application allows a user to record a desired note or comment along with a title or category for easy recognition. Users can enter notes to be saved to a database and update any notes as needed.

Secure Password Generator


https://github.com/dawsontc003/secure-password-generator/

https://dawsontc003.github.io/secure-password-generator/

The Secured Password generator website is useful to users who understand the value of a secure password. This application takes desired inputs from a user such as character length and character type to generate a random sucure password. This will ensure passwords are not easily discovered based on personal knowledge of which typically allows passwords to be hacked.
